1
00:01:52,870 --> 00:01:55,039
The medicines prescribed for
His Majesty have had no effect.

2
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:57,150
What should we do?

3
00:01:57,150 --> 00:01:58,950
I'm afraid this may cause chaos.

4
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:01,920
Lord Zhang, Lord Li.

5
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,430
How is His Majesty?

6
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:04,590
Nothing serious,

7
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,680
just a minor illness.

8
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:09,190
But I heard from an imperial physician

9
00:02:09,190 --> 00:02:10,990
that His Majesty is gravely ill.

10
00:02:11,590 --> 00:02:12,840
If he doesn't recover soon,

11
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,080
then... -How dare you!

12
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:16,000
Who spouted such nonsense?

13
00:02:16,030 --> 00:02:18,470
I'll have his entire clan executed
for His Majesty.

14
00:02:18,470 --> 00:02:19,240
My lords,

15
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:21,840
you are all
important ministers in the court,

16
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,400
holding positions of great authority.

17
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,660
How can you believe every rumor you hear?

18
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:29,880
I was appointed Chief Grand Secretary
by the late emperor himself.

19
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:31,870
If my words carry no weight with you,

20
00:02:31,870 --> 00:02:32,840
would you really

21
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:35,470
place your trust in an imperial physician?

22
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:36,590
Lord Li.

23
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:39,750
We must severely punish those
who deceive the public.

24
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:40,560
Yes.

25
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:41,960
My lords,

26
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,150
go back.

27
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:45,410
Court will convene as usual tomorrow.

28
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:47,280
If anyone dares neglect his duties,

29
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:49,400
I will show no mercy.

30
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:50,750
Yes.

31
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,750
You may leave now.

32
00:02:54,190 --> 00:02:55,079
Your Majesty.

33
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:56,840
What happened to you?

34
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,800
Wake up and look at me.

35
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:03,680
What happened to you?

36
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:11,800
Wake up and look at me.

37
00:03:13,190 --> 00:03:15,000
The imperial physicians say
there's no hope for you—

38
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,120
but how can that be?

39
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,190
Liu Chu.

40
00:03:19,470 --> 00:03:20,470
Wake up.

41
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:24,280
Look at me.

42
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:27,030
I am Jiang Wanyu.

43
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,590
Open your eyes.

44
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:34,750
Liu Chu.

45
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:37,720
Did I not decree that

46
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,630
no one is to approach

47
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:40,630
His Majesty without my order?

48
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:41,910
But...

49
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:43,190
Consort Ling is...

50
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,630
And you still dare to make excuses?

51
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:45,520
Get out.

52
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,050
Give yourself forty slaps.

53
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:48,000
Yes.

54
00:03:52,030 --> 00:03:52,870
Xie.

55
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:55,960
Don't be too sad.

56
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,750
The imperial physicians
are trying to find a way.

57
00:03:57,750 --> 00:04:00,000
But they all say there's no hope for him.

58
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:04,470
You are with child.

59
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,360
Be careful not to harm the fetus.

60
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:07,960
Guards,

61
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,280
escort Consort Ling back to her palace

62
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,680
and take good care of her.

63
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:11,960
Xie.

64
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:12,560
I...

65
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,010
You are His Majesty's consort,

66
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:17,040
and you are carrying his child.

67
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:18,630
At all times,

68
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:20,630
you must put the imperial heir first.

69
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:21,690
Do you understand?

70
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:24,000
I want to stay with him a little longer.

71
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:29,810
Your Highness.

72
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:32,680
Your Highness.

73
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:34,560
Let's go, Your Highness.

74
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,000
This prescription is too strong.

75
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,870
I suggest adding Scutellaria

76
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:53,070
for it to take effect.

77
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,360
No, no.

78
00:04:54,510 --> 00:04:56,270
Scutellaria is too strong.

79
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,890
It may harm His Majesty.

80
00:04:57,950 --> 00:05:00,630
We should replace it with Forsythia.

81
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:02,070
Dandelion can also detoxify.

82
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:03,270
We might as well include it as well.

83
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:04,630
I still think Scutellaria is better.

84
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:05,480
My lords.

85
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,000
If I may be blunt,

86
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,680
while your prescriptions are sound,

87
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:11,160
they may not be suitable for
His Majesty's current condition.

88
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,190
Who are you

89
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:14,000
to interfere here?

90
00:05:14,070 --> 00:05:15,510
How dare you question us?

91
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:18,160
This is Han Yunling, who cured the plague

92
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,290
in Huangpi Village.

93
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,190
But it doesn't mean

94
00:05:21,190 --> 00:05:22,750
she can cure His Majesty.

95
00:05:22,950 --> 00:05:24,800
What this physician says is reasonable.

96
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:27,270
But you've been arguing here
for so long without any result.

97
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:29,190
If you are willing to hear me out,

98
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:30,480
we may be able to find

99
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,010
a more suitable treatment.

100
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,270
We veteran imperial physicians

101
00:05:35,270 --> 00:05:36,830
have served His Majesty for years.

102
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:37,800
Why should we

103
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:40,070
listen to a mere girl like you?

104
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:41,630
Medicine has no rank

105
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:42,800
or gender.

106
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,830
Everyone here is an esteemed physician.

107
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:45,800
What's more,

108
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,240
the poison in Huangpi Village

109
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,680
that left everyone helpless

110
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,870
was cured by Physician Han here.

111
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,630
If none of you have a solution,

112
00:05:54,070 --> 00:05:55,390
why not let me try?

113
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:04,830
Physician Han.

114
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,430
These are His Majesty's

115
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:09,040
full symptoms and treatment records.

116
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:11,480
He first fell into a coma,

117
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:15,070
followed by a persistent low-grade fever,

118
00:06:15,070 --> 00:06:18,070
and now he has widespread bruising.

119
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,720
Could you please

120
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,800
elaborate further on

121
00:06:23,070 --> 00:06:25,430
the medications His Majesty has taken
and their effects?

122
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:27,360
He was first given a heat-clearing

123
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,290
and exterior-releasing formula,

124
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:31,480
but it had little effect.

125
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:33,360
We then tried

126
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:35,480
a prescription
for nourishing qi and blood.

127
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,480
His Majesty's strength recovered a bit,

128
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:40,390
but his condition didn't improve at all.

129
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:42,800
You've explained it in such detail.

130
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,750
It seems you've put a lot of work into it.

131
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:46,480
You flatter me, Physician Han.

132
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,830
I once had the honor

133
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:50,830
of serving as an assistant
to the previous Physician Han,

134
00:06:50,830 --> 00:06:51,920
so I would never be negligent

135
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,430
in matters of diagnosis.

136
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,000
You are

137
00:06:57,870 --> 00:06:59,390
Uncle Song?

138
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,070
Yes.

139
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,680
It's been years.

140
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,480
You've grown into a young woman.

141
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:08,240
I didn't expect that
after all these years,

142
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:10,430
my father's medical skills
are still recognized.

143
00:07:10,430 --> 00:07:11,920
What happened to the Han family

144
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,380
back then was suspicious.

145
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:16,430
I believe the truth will come out one day.

146
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,240
Physician Han, your identity—

147
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,680
I will keep it strictly confidential.

148
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:33,600
Have you remembered everything?

149
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,310
No.

150
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:49,070
Is there anything unusual
in the medical records?

151
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:50,680
None.

152
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:51,870
All treatments

153
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,480
followed standard procedures,

154
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,800
yet His Majesty's condition

155
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:56,390
has not improved.

156
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:58,290
That means our approach is wrong.

157
00:07:58,950 --> 00:08:00,870
What caused his coma

158
00:08:00,870 --> 00:08:01,830
is not illness—

159
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,600
but poison.

160
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:05,680
Poison?

161
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,290
Do you have a way?

162
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:10,800
I can only try my best.

163
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:13,430
Xiao Chi.

164
00:08:14,070 --> 00:08:15,390
Can you bring me the list

165
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:17,000
of tribute gifts from all countries,

166
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,480
along with His Majesty's daily records.

167
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,630
I want to see them.

168
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:20,560
Tributes?

169
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:24,230
You think there is a problem
with the tributes?

170
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,720
But these tributes

171
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,750
have always been checked by Zheng.

172
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,870
There can't be any problems.

173
00:08:29,870 --> 00:08:31,680
I know Lord Fei would never do anything

174
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,440
to hurt your brotherly bond.

175
00:08:33,789 --> 00:08:35,669
But even the most careful person

176
00:08:35,669 --> 00:08:37,240
can make mistakes.

177
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,080
I proposed inspecting the tributes

178
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:41,240
just to clear Lord Fei of suspicion

179
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,360
and to prevent others
from exploiting the situation.

180
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:45,490
It would be bad if Lord Fei were framed.

181
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:46,960
Okay.

182
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:49,260
I'll find someone to get them.

183
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:04,080
Did you poison Liu Chu?

184
00:09:05,630 --> 00:09:06,630
What do you think?

185
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:09,000
Was it really Jiang Wanyu?

186
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:13,080
Jiang Wanyu knew nothing about it.

187
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:15,760
Then who could it be?

188
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:20,010
The Hall Master has sent
another spy into the palace?

189
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,220
Are you scared?

190
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:24,670
Of course I am.

191
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,790
In Caidie Hall,

192
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:28,530
once a spy is no longer useful,

193
00:09:28,670 --> 00:09:30,080
there is only death.

194
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,970
Where are you going?

195
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:36,550
I'll go beg the Hall Master
for another chance.

196
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,360
Jin Xi.

197
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:40,000
Stop aiding and abetting evil.

198
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,630
I have no other choice.

199
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:42,360
Fei Zheng.

200
00:09:42,750 --> 00:09:43,880
I need the antidote.

201
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,640
But the Hall Master no longer trusts me.

202
00:09:47,030 --> 00:09:48,360
If I don't go and beg her,

203
00:09:49,750 --> 00:09:51,270
I'll be as good as dead.

204
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,730
I can give you the antidote.

205
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,840
You still have it?

206
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,600
I already took that one.

207
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,370
This is another one.

208
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:09,340
The Hall Master only gave you one.

209
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:11,790
Just like you said,

210
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:14,390
as long as I still have value,

211
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:16,080
asking for another antidote

212
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:17,270
is not difficult.

213
00:10:18,030 --> 00:10:18,630
Take it.

214
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,210
Aren't you afraid?

215
00:10:20,750 --> 00:10:22,030
Take this,

216
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,690
then go back to Changmo.

217
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:28,000
I don't want to owe you.

218
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,630
I'll find my own way

219
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:30,920
to get the antidote.

220
00:10:32,390 --> 00:10:33,200
Jin Xi.

221
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,080
Hall Master.

222
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,870
Liu Chu has been poisoned

223
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:47,670
and is still unconscious.

224
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:50,240
He is said to have multiple bruises.

225
00:10:51,750 --> 00:10:52,630
It seems

226
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:54,690
you're more useful than some others.

227
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:56,670
Come here.

228
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,390
Thank you, Hall Master.

229
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:09,480
What do you need me for?

230
00:11:09,630 --> 00:11:11,030
I'll do whatever it takes,

231
00:11:11,030 --> 00:11:12,490
even at the cost of my life.

232
00:11:12,870 --> 00:11:14,800
Liu Chu has already been poisoned.

233
00:11:56,870 --> 00:11:58,790
You've only just recovered.

234
00:11:58,790 --> 00:12:00,360
Go back and rest.

235
00:12:00,790 --> 00:12:01,600
No need.

236
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,770
I'll stay here with you.

237
00:12:17,030 --> 00:12:17,510
Here,

238
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:18,750
have some hot tea.

239
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,630
My lords,

240
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:16,790
His Majesty is unwell.

241
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,910
Many court matters will need

242
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:22,320
your decision and handling, Lord Zhang.

243
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:25,910
Does anyone

244
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:29,000
have matters to report?

245
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:36,770
What Jinglan needs most right now

246
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:38,150
is stability.

247
00:14:38,150 --> 00:14:40,000
His Majesty has yet to wake.

248
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:42,000
Forgive my treasonous words—

249
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:44,720
but if something were to happen…

250
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:46,870
I mean, just hypothetically…

251
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:47,860
Lord Zhang.

252
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,630
You are the Chief Grand Secretary.

253
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:51,910
Some matters cannot be considered lightly,

254
00:14:51,910 --> 00:14:54,240
but they also cannot be ignored.

255
00:14:54,630 --> 00:14:55,510
What do you think?

256
00:14:55,510 --> 00:14:58,030
They risk their lives

257
00:14:58,030 --> 00:14:59,790
and say such things,

258
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:02,630
they could be considered
loyal ministers of Jinglan.

259
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:03,440
Lord Li.

260
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:06,120
What do you mean by this?

261
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:09,000
Nothing.

262
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:11,000
Just honest advice.

263
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:11,720
Lord Fei,

264
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:13,550
don't be angry.

265
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:14,390
Indeed.

266
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:16,030
Could His Majesty's illness

267
00:15:16,030 --> 00:15:17,960
have something to do with Lord Fei?

268
00:15:19,790 --> 00:15:21,720
If you have something to say,

269
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:23,440
just speak frankly.

270
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:25,320
In fact, we find

271
00:15:25,390 --> 00:15:27,790
His Majesty's illness rather suspicious.

272
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:29,910
Ever since you and Xiao Chi

273
00:15:29,910 --> 00:15:31,440
returned from Tianlang Pass,

274
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,630
strange things

275
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,440
have been happening in Jinglan.

276
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:35,270
Yes.

277
00:15:35,670 --> 00:15:36,390
First the incident in Huangpi Village,

278
00:15:36,390 --> 00:15:38,240
then Xiao Chi,

279
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:40,120
and now His Majesty.

280
00:15:40,120 --> 00:15:42,630
It's hard not to find this suspicious.

281
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:43,600
That's right.

282
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:46,440
I heard that the one treating His Majesty

283
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:49,600
is the woman who returned
from Changmo with you.

284
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:50,630
Lord Fei,

285
00:15:50,870 --> 00:15:54,150
that makes you look suspect
of colluding with outsiders.

286
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:54,750
Everyone.

287
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:55,750
Alright.

288
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:57,840
The court

289
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:59,970
is not a place for you to pass judgment.

290
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:03,240
His Majesty's condition is still unknown,

291
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:06,240
yet you're already
suspecting senior ministers.

292
00:16:06,390 --> 00:16:07,990
What kind of conduct is this?

293
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:09,480
Lord Zhang

294
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,910
is right.

295
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:14,550
But what you said is also reasonable.

296
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,520
If His Majesty's illness

297
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:19,360
is truly related to Fei Zheng, Xiao Chi,

298
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:21,510
and Han Yunling,

299
00:16:21,630 --> 00:16:23,830
then we might as well interrogate them.

300
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:26,600
Maybe we can find some clues.

301
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:32,750
How dare you

302
00:16:32,910 --> 00:16:34,510
spread rumors in the court!

303
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:58,790
Your Highness.

304
00:16:59,030 --> 00:17:01,550
The court ministers
are all in heated debate.

305
00:17:01,550 --> 00:17:02,750
What are they saying?

306
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:04,030
They say that

307
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,160
if

308
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:06,790
His Majesty does not wake up…

309
00:17:10,109 --> 00:17:11,310
Just a group of treacherous officials

310
00:17:11,310 --> 00:17:12,369
spreading rumors.

311
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:13,880
They should

312
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:15,440
all be executed.

313
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:18,109
Fortunately,
Lord Zhang stabilized the situation,

314
00:17:18,109 --> 00:17:20,790
with General Xiao and Lord Fei's support.

315
00:17:21,349 --> 00:17:22,640
In times like this,

316
00:17:22,790 --> 00:17:24,310
no one can be trusted.

317
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:27,750
General Xiao and Lord Fei
hold you in high regard,

318
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:29,960
and they share a deep brotherly bond
with His Majesty.

319
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:32,200
They are unlikely to act as you fear.

320
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:35,640
Everyone grows up,

321
00:17:36,550 --> 00:17:38,240
and people can change.

322
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:42,790
Have the Xieying Guard get ready.

323
00:17:42,790 --> 00:17:44,400
If anything happens in the palace,

324
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,660
we can respond in time.

325
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:46,640
Yes.

326
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:52,240
Some ministers' objections

327
00:17:52,240 --> 00:17:53,790
are not without reason.

328
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,400
If this has nothing to do with you,

329
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:58,110
then you must find a way

330
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:00,040
to prove your innocence.

331
00:18:00,550 --> 00:18:02,160
If we cure His Majesty,

332
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:03,640
that will prove our innocence.

333
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:04,960
In that case,

334
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:06,240
I am quite curious.

335
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:07,400
What kind of illness

336
00:18:07,400 --> 00:18:09,130
is His Majesty suffering from?

337
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:11,110
It is not an ordinary illness.

338
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:14,270
It is a rare poison.

339
00:18:15,240 --> 00:18:16,110
Poison?

340
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:22,790
Since His Majesty has been poisoned
by something so rare,

341
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:25,000
how can he be cured?

342
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:26,590
This is no ordinary poison.

343
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:28,850
It requires an extraordinary remedy.

344
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,440
I have already found a clue,

345
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:33,310
and discussed it with General Xiao.

346
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,640
Rest assured, my lords.

347
00:18:34,640 --> 00:18:35,790
With me,

348
00:18:35,830 --> 00:18:37,350
the truth will be found

349
00:18:37,350 --> 00:18:39,010
and His Majesty will be cured.

350
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:46,110
Your Highness.

351
00:18:48,590 --> 00:18:50,320
His Majesty has been poisoned.

352
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:53,350
Poisoned?

353
00:19:07,110 --> 00:19:08,240
By order of the Eldest Princess,

354
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:09,440
from today on,

355
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:11,000
you are confined to the Consort's Palace

356
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,200
and may not leave.

357
00:19:13,030 --> 00:19:13,590
Lan.

358
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:14,790
Why am I confined?

359
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:16,550
His Majesty is unconscious.

360
00:19:16,550 --> 00:19:20,080
All related persons are to be confined
pending investigation.

361
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:24,590
Lan!

362
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:26,240
Lan.

363
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:27,110
Lan!

364
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:28,640
Take me to see Her Highness.

365
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:30,240
Lan!

366
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:32,110
Lan!

367
00:19:32,350 --> 00:19:34,830
I want to see Her Highness.

368
00:19:34,830 --> 00:19:37,440
What exactly happened to His Majesty?

369
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:40,640
I want to see him.

370
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:42,350
Lan.

371
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:12,240
It's getting late.

372
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:13,400
Go back and rest.

373
00:20:13,790 --> 00:20:15,190
I will stay here tonight.

374
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:17,110
You were on watch yesterday.

375
00:20:17,110 --> 00:20:18,790
Let me do it today.

376
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,310
Then why not

377
00:20:21,750 --> 00:20:22,400
both of us

378
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:24,200
stay?

379
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:27,110
I'm sure Chu

380
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:28,610
would agree as well.

381
00:20:33,590 --> 00:20:34,310
Why

382
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:35,960
don't we

383
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:37,640
have a drink with him?

384
00:20:38,790 --> 00:20:39,550
Guards!

385
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:40,440
Yes.

386
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:41,780
Bring the wine.

387
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:48,790
Please.

388
00:21:04,030 --> 00:21:04,750
Chu.

389
00:21:05,350 --> 00:21:06,720
Look, Xiao Chi has already

390
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:07,960
poured you a drink.

391
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:09,160
Get well soon.

392
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:11,160
And get up and drink it.

393
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,000
Come on,

394
00:21:12,310 --> 00:21:13,440
today the three of us

395
00:21:13,790 --> 00:21:15,190
will drink until we drop.

396
00:21:16,790 --> 00:21:17,920
Drink until we drop.

397
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:27,030
We grew up together

398
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:29,720
and

399
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:31,770
went through many hardships.

400
00:21:32,030 --> 00:21:33,350
Our brotherhood

401
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,030
is what I value most.

402
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,310
This cup

403
00:21:38,790 --> 00:21:40,110
is for you two.

404
00:21:42,790 --> 00:21:43,640
Please.

405
00:21:52,550 --> 00:21:53,790
You two may leave.

406
00:21:53,790 --> 00:21:54,270
Yes.

407
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:58,270
Lord Li,

408
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,790
what do you mean?

409
00:21:59,790 --> 00:22:00,680
Lord Zhang,

410
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:02,310
I've come to pay my respects.

411
00:22:02,920 --> 00:22:03,720
Look—

412
00:22:03,750 --> 00:22:06,160
these are rare
surviving copies of ancient books

413
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:07,400
from across the country
and various dynasties

414
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:10,240
that I've collected for you.

415
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:12,960
Such good books

416
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:15,510
should be given to
those who appreciate them.

417
00:22:15,510 --> 00:22:18,110
Keeping them at my place
would be a waste,

418
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:19,880
so I've brought them to you.

419
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:24,000
Lord Li.

420
00:22:24,750 --> 00:22:27,160
His Majesty is still unconscious.

421
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:30,350
How can I be in the mood to read?

422
00:22:31,110 --> 00:22:32,160
Right.

423
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:34,000
That...

424
00:22:34,310 --> 00:22:35,350
that is another important reason

425
00:22:35,350 --> 00:22:37,030
why I am here.

426
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:42,440
If His Majesty were truly…

427
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:46,680
I mean,

428
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:48,110
of course he is blessed

429
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:49,350
and will be fine.

430
00:22:49,830 --> 00:22:51,510
But some things

431
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:53,510
must be considered in advance.

432
00:22:55,350 --> 00:22:56,680
I also hope

433
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:59,720
to find answers in these books.

434
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:01,550
Lord Zhang.

435
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,160
I've arranged

436
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,920
these ancient books

437
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,590
for you by dynasty.

438
00:23:06,590 --> 00:23:07,590
You can go through them carefully

439
00:23:07,590 --> 00:23:09,790
when you have time.

440
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:11,590
In fact,

441
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:12,480
I believe

442
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:13,650
you've already

443
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:16,510
understood many things in your heart.

444
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:19,240
Yes.

445
00:23:21,030 --> 00:23:22,590
If His Majesty

446
00:23:23,030 --> 00:23:24,920
never wakes up,

447
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:28,310
once Consort Ling gives birth,

448
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:31,370
I will support
the only remaining heir of the Liu family

449
00:23:31,550 --> 00:23:34,440
to keep Jinglan prosperous.

450
00:23:35,590 --> 00:23:37,000
That may be so,

451
00:23:37,030 --> 00:23:38,920
but we don't even know

452
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:40,920
whether the child is a boy or a girl.

453
00:23:41,310 --> 00:23:42,790
And even if it is a boy,

454
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,640
whether he can survive

455
00:23:44,830 --> 00:23:46,790
is still uncertain.

456
00:23:50,240 --> 00:23:51,830
So what do you mean?

457
00:23:53,750 --> 00:23:55,310
I mean,

458
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:57,790
The Liu family and Jinglan

459
00:23:58,440 --> 00:24:00,200
are two different things.

460
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:03,550
I know you are loyal

461
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:05,640
to the late Emperor and the Liu family.

462
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,270
But

463
00:24:06,790 --> 00:24:08,790
if the Liu bloodline truly dies out,

464
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:11,510
what will happen to Jinglan?

465
00:24:11,510 --> 00:24:13,030
To the people?

466
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:15,110
And to the court?

467
00:24:20,350 --> 00:24:22,240
This is too tricky.

468
00:24:23,510 --> 00:24:25,480
So what do you

469
00:24:26,110 --> 00:24:27,200
really mean?

470
00:24:36,350 --> 00:24:38,240
My real meaning is…

471
00:24:40,790 --> 00:24:41,720
Lord Zhang.

472
00:24:42,110 --> 00:24:44,400
You are the head of the ministers.

473
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:49,400
If the Liu bloodline truly dies out,

474
00:24:49,550 --> 00:24:50,750
wouldn't this empire

475
00:24:51,240 --> 00:24:53,000
be yours?

476
00:24:53,750 --> 00:24:54,310
You...

477
00:24:54,960 --> 00:24:58,160
How dare you say such treasonous words!

478
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,590
Right.

479
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:03,790
We are both assistant ministers.

480
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:05,720
You've always been thoughtful.

481
00:25:05,880 --> 00:25:07,270
It's only right for you

482
00:25:08,000 --> 00:25:09,350
to think ahead.

483
00:25:09,350 --> 00:25:11,080
I'm just doing this for Jinglan

484
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:13,400
and for the people.

485
00:25:19,350 --> 00:25:20,160
Lord Li.

486
00:25:21,030 --> 00:25:21,590
Lord Li,

487
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:22,960
what's wrong?

488
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:24,790
Don't panic, Lord Zhang.

489
00:25:24,790 --> 00:25:25,480
Lord Li.

490
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:26,310
I'm fine.

491
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:29,790
It's probably just that
His Majesty's poor health

492
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:32,400
has been keeping me restless,

493
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:35,200
and this chest pain
may have flared up again.

494
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:36,830
Then

495
00:25:36,830 --> 00:25:38,400
hurry back to your residence and rest.

496
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:41,400
We still have to go to the palace
to see His Majesty tomorrow.

497
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:42,440
Okay.

498
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,510
Take care.

499
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:45,400
Just go.

500
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:46,310
Sorry.

501
00:25:46,590 --> 00:25:48,240
I will take my leave now.

502
00:25:51,270 --> 00:25:52,240
Look.

503
00:25:55,070 --> 00:25:56,030
Lord Li.

504
00:25:56,400 --> 00:25:57,440
Your books.

505
00:26:00,510 --> 00:26:03,200
These are not gold or silver,

506
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:05,640
merely courtesies among gentlemen.

507
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:08,550
They won't ruin
your reputation, Lord Zhang.

508
00:26:08,550 --> 00:26:09,200
Don't worry.

509
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:10,240
All right.

510
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,900
Then I'll accept them for now.

511
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:14,830
I'll read them

512
00:26:14,830 --> 00:26:16,400
after His Majesty awakens.

513
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:19,640
I shall take my leave.

514
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:21,200
Take care.

515
00:26:47,640 --> 00:26:48,550
Chu.

516
00:26:48,830 --> 00:26:50,550
Get up and look at Xiao Chi.

517
00:26:50,720 --> 00:26:52,030
He seems troubled.

518
00:26:52,750 --> 00:26:53,640
General Xiao,

519
00:26:53,920 --> 00:26:56,510
why don't you tell your thoughts

520
00:26:56,510 --> 00:26:57,720
to Chu?

521
00:26:57,830 --> 00:26:59,630
He is now the ruler of the nation.

522
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:00,830
Whatever you want,

523
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:02,310
he can fulfill it.

524
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:07,190
I was just thinking about

525
00:27:08,350 --> 00:27:10,410
the three of us when we were children.

526
00:27:10,550 --> 00:27:11,750
Back then,

527
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,460
Chu led us everywhere,

528
00:27:14,110 --> 00:27:15,640
and we were completely carefree.

529
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:16,900
It was such a good time.

530
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:33,160
Chu.

531
00:27:33,440 --> 00:27:34,830
Get up and take a look.

532
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,480
Our dear Zheng

533
00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:38,030
is troubled too.

534
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:42,330
You've married the woman you love,

535
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:43,640
and I'm just

536
00:27:48,790 --> 00:27:49,720
waiting for you

537
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:50,830
to wake up

538
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:53,310
and arrange a marriage for our Lord Fei.

539
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,510
I don't need

540
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:04,290
any arranged marriage.

541
00:28:07,110 --> 00:28:08,510
In my life,

542
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:09,830
with you,

543
00:28:10,830 --> 00:28:12,720
and Liu Chu as my brothers,

544
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:16,640
that is enough.

545
00:28:21,350 --> 00:28:22,610
I ask for nothing more.

546
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,140
Please.

547
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:37,000
What's wrong?

548
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:39,440
Nothing.

549
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:46,730
You're coughing blood,

550
00:28:46,830 --> 00:28:48,230
and you say it's nothing?

551
00:28:49,030 --> 00:28:50,030
It's an old issue.

552
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:52,640
Ever since I was poisoned last time,

553
00:28:54,030 --> 00:28:55,310
it's been acting up.

554
00:28:55,550 --> 00:28:56,350
I just

555
00:28:57,110 --> 00:28:58,710
have occasional flare-ups.

556
00:29:00,440 --> 00:29:01,510
Wait here for me.

557
00:29:01,960 --> 00:29:03,640
I'll go get Physician Han to check on you.

558
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:04,440
Zheng.

559
00:29:04,920 --> 00:29:06,400
Don't tell Han Yunling.

560
00:29:07,110 --> 00:29:08,510
I don't want her to worry.

561
00:29:09,030 --> 00:29:09,750
Besides,

562
00:29:10,750 --> 00:29:12,110
she has to find a way

563
00:29:12,590 --> 00:29:13,640
to treat Chu.

564
00:29:18,790 --> 00:29:19,750
Look at you.

565
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:20,920
I'm fine.

566
00:29:21,830 --> 00:29:22,550
I won't die.

567
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:24,160
Come on.

568
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:25,310
Today,

569
00:29:25,590 --> 00:29:26,830
let's drink until we drop.

570
00:29:26,830 --> 00:29:27,720
We'll deal with

571
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:30,770
everything else tomorrow.

572
00:29:36,030 --> 00:29:36,790
Fine.

573
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,510
You're in this condition

574
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:41,840
and still want to drink?

575
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:44,030
You really have a death wish.

576
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:48,160
We'll talk about everything else

577
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:49,160
tomorrow.

578
00:29:49,640 --> 00:29:50,720
Okay.
